Package: cansim
Type: Package
Title: Convenience function to download Cansim tables
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jens von Bergmann <jens@mountainmath.ca>
Maintainer: Jens von Bergmann <jens@mountainmath.ca>
Description: Downloads Cansim data into a tidy data frame,
    deals with encoding, allows for English or French language data,
    has a convenience function to scale numerical values
